stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> FREE

    FREE --> RESERVED_D2H: RequestOffload lease granted
    RESERVED_D2H --> D2H_IN_FLIGHT: rank launches cudaMemcpyAsync D2H
    D2H_IN_FLIGHT --> PINNED_VALID: rank CUDA event complete

    PINNED_VALID --> DRAIN_IN_FLIGHT: daemon background drain
    DRAIN_IN_FLIGHT --> COLD_VALID_PAGEABLE: drain to pageable DRAM complete
    DRAIN_IN_FLIGHT --> COLD_VALID_NVME: drain to NVMe complete
    COLD_VALID_PAGEABLE --> FREE: pinned slot released
    COLD_VALID_NVME --> FREE: pinned slot released

    COLD_VALID_PAGEABLE --> READBACK_IN_FLIGHT: prefetch request
    COLD_VALID_NVME --> READBACK_IN_FLIGHT: prefetch request
    READBACK_IN_FLIGHT --> PINNED_VALID: cold -> pinned complete

    PINNED_VALID --> H2D_IN_FLIGHT: rank launches cudaMemcpyAsync H2D
    H2D_IN_FLIGHT --> GPU_VALID: rank CUDA event complete
    GPU_VALID --> FREE: release pinned slot if cold copy retained

    RESERVED_D2H --> ERROR: timeout/rank failure
    D2H_IN_FLIGHT --> ERROR: timeout/rank failure
    DRAIN_IN_FLIGHT --> ERROR: IO failure
    READBACK_IN_FLIGHT --> ERROR: IO failure
    H2D_IN_FLIGHT --> ERROR: timeout/rank failure
